@Realjohndoe: 
> You trick them into being HOmo's. 
... you *are* aware I'm already gay, right? And that I wasn't "tricked" into being so?

@Clearnet is Bad: that still doesn't fix my hangups with ActivityPub, mainly that I can't [forcibly purge](/1MeeJWbbQHArbqD6UUHSjh9EVycvnTUBFa/archive/blog/2019/march/zotland.html) my deactivated accounts from other instances, I can't run everything behind Tor/I2P and still retain a reasonable amount of connectivity, and that it's still a glorified server/client setup. And that there's not a lot to do on the fediverse other than idle chit-chat. "Nice" isn't enough of a qualifier for me to invest my precious time in people I don't know, and my time on leftist instances leads me to believe "accepting" crumbles into a hugbox facade as soon as I step outside of the acceptable party lines.

(Disclaimer: the above linked post is a little outdated, since I use neither Zot nor [Gopher](/1MeeJWbbQHArbqD6UUHSjh9EVycvnTUBFa/archive/blog/2019/december/death-of-a-gopher.html) anymore.)

If you could shoot me an email at vanevander(at)mayvaneday.art with who you thought I was, that would be great, since if there's someone trying to impersonate me I'd like to know about it. Don't worry about the assocation since I won't bother trying to connect the two.
